just include the following css in your header if you want to debug (I got it from the author @ https://medium.freecodecamp.org/heres-my-favorite-weird-trick-to-debug-css-88529aa5a6a3 ):

*:not(path):not(g) {
    color:                    hsla(210, 100%, 100%, 0.9) !important;
    background:               hsla(210, 100%,  50%, 0.5) !important;
    outline:    solid 0.25rem hsla(210, 100%, 100%, 0.5) !important;
    box-shadow: none !important;
}

